<title>PATHIAN CU THANGTHAT SI KO SEH CH1</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zeizong sertu Pathian, thangthat si ko seh, Vawlei a dawt ca'h a Fa-pa
 a kan pek; Sual ngaihthiam-nak ca a nunnak kha a sian, Mi kip ca'h a
 nunnak kutka a hun cang.

[C1]
   Bawipa cu, thangthat u, Khua zakip cul dih seh, Bawipa cu, thangthat
   u, Mi kip i lawm hna seh, Fapa Jesuh thawngin Pathian cu panh u. Zeizong
   vialte sertu Pathian thangthat u.

[V2]
 Maw Khamhnak tling thisen in a kan tlanhnak, A zummi kip sin i Pathian
 biakamnak; Lungtak in a zummi misual bik hmanh nih, Jesuh sinin sual
 ngaihthiamnak a hmuh colh.

[C2]
   Bawipa cu, thangthat u, Khua zakip cul dih seh, Bawipa cu, thangthat
   u, Mi kip i lawm hna seh, Fapa Jesuh thawngin Pathian cu panh u. Zeizong
   vialte sertu Pathian thangthat u.

[V3]
 A sermi thil vialte kong a kan cawnpiak, Fapa Jesuh thawngin lawmhnak
 a sang chin; Sihmanhseh Jesuh kan hmuh te tikah cun, Khuaruahhar in
 lawmhnak a sang chinchin lai.

[C3]
   Bawipa cu, thangthat u, Khua zakip cul dih seh, Bawipa cu, thangthat
   u, Mi kip i lawm hna seh, Fapa Jesuh thawngin Pathian cu panh u. Zeizong
   vialte sertu Pathian thangthat u.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>